Hollywood actor of Nigerian origin, John Boyega has bought his parents a mansion in London, United Kingdom, and their reaction is priceless. In the video posted on social media, the actor took his parents to a house under the guise they were coming for an interview. They never knew they were being taken to their own private mansion. While seated at the ‘venue’ awaiting the commencement of the interview, the actor revealed to them there was no interview and he has only brought them to their own house. John took to his Instagram to share a video of the special moment and he wrote: “Moments like these make all the hard work worth it.” See Post: John Boyega bought his mother and father a house & their reaction…We’re not crying, you are 🥺❤️ pic.twitter.com/tL0LrVp3fE Source